ygData.messageBody:
It seems that the only one I can find is the Necro Fire Beetle Eye quest on
the top floor of the Shadow Knight/Necro guildhouse. Other than that, nobody
talks to me when I hail them. It may be because of our Faction/Class/Level.

Zaratul D'vorn
